  speakerName: "Anlat\u0131c\u0131"
  dialogueText: "Ne yaz\u0131k ki adam c\xFCmlesini tamamlayacak kadar uzun hayata
    tutunamad\u0131. K\u0131sa bir s\xFCre sonra g\xF6zlerini yumdu."
  choice1Text: "\"Umar\u0131m Tanr\u0131lar\u0131n kutsal krall\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
    tekrar kar\u015F\u0131la\u015F\u0131r\u0131z. Huzur i\xE7inde yat.\""
